{"tid":1596893,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"千祈唔好對話，你地醒未啊香港人","createTime":"2019-09-26T16:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T17:15:43.000Z","uid":41458,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"23eb8e52fcd6f8fbdad60fdd41b38c3169a6966e","tid":1596893,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:57:11.000Z","msg":"請你地好好認識中共嘅歷史<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">對話係冇可能有任何正面作用！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n由得佢自己請班藍屍對飽佢<br />\n我地連睇都唔洗睇，更加唔洗討論<br />\n<br />\n請各位香港人及早醒覺<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港問題在於制度</span></span></strong><br />\n而<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">現行嘅制度下，冇可能有任何改變做到</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n因為政府只聽命於中共<br />\n中共對權力係唔會放手<br />\n視人民生命如糞土<br />\n<br />\n對話只會將香港人帶入去下一個深淵<br />\n千祈唔好再同政府對話<br />\n<br />\n光復香港！"},{"pid":"f1fd6ea3fd5aaf3c6f6ed0849ae4b482397664d8","tid":1596893,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:58:55.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n[文宣] 我哋好似忘記咗其中一條重要戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592692</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b8e98873718831ac074cfc706b4f182201961734","tid":1596893,"uid":327013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:59:23.000Z","msg":"毋忘歷史上條柒婆嘅socall對話係咩料啦香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家仲未知死?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jume5fX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJume5fX.jpg&h=d1f55898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gZYAPHD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgZYAPHD.jpg&h=48e68d94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A9E4H2D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/